        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">How much house can you afford?</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/rent-vs-buy-calculator/" class="flex flex-col gap-1 p-4 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl hover:border-indigo-400 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
